{"tid":1535441,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大門深鎖、人去樓空 《路透》曝上海自貿區慘況","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:12:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":256,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"2acf7558b4f062badbee7788e27dd7ac45a52b91","tid":1535441,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/09/02/phpoDStFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2FphpoDStFV.jpg&h=0c71a6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國的「上海自由貿易試驗區」2013年推行時曾喧騰一時，也曾引發各種討論，當時官員曾宣稱這將吸引更多外國投資，深化與週遭各國的貿易關係，不過6年過去後，當《路透》實地探訪時，卻發現此地現在已是「環堵蕭然」的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》在以「銀行離去徒留殭屍帳戶 中國上海自貿區發展艱難」為題的報導中這樣描述現在上海自貿區的「上海外高橋保稅區」：「辦公室人去樓空，玻璃大門深鎖，椅子胡亂堆疊，曾經上班族人滿為患的食堂，進駐餐館一間一間關門，用過的筷子及塑膠餐具散亂在地。」<br />\n<br />\n上海華瑞銀行在上海自貿區的業務傳出不振，招商銀行據傳已經解散自貿區業務團隊，寧波銀行在自貿區有4間分行，但基本上只執行一般銀行業務，自貿區的帳戶基本不太使用，成為「殭屍帳戶」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，除了因美中貿易戰而導致的經濟放緩以外，造成上海自貿區這種慘況的理由，更多來自當局對資本的管控：雖然2013年自貿區成立時，中國官員曾承諾更自由的貨幣流通及更簡便的國際貿易，但事實上卻反其道而行，使企業逐步離開自貿區。<br />\n<br />\n寧波銀行內部人士曾抱怨，自貿區帳戶不但每筆交易都要上報，而且還不能與普通帳戶共用，「根本無用」；南京銀行內部人士則批評，自貿區業務比較像在服務政府目標，而非商業機會；上海財經大學教授丁劍平則直言，上海自貿區現在已「不再便捷」。<br />\n<br />\n東方資本研究公司（Orient Capital Research）總經理克立爾（Andrew Collier）認為，上海自貿區減少地方政府稅收，且與政府阻止資金外流的目標矛盾，使得難以達成政府想要的效果，即使有新的自貿區也一樣。"},{"pid":"9660993983aab6e818031ac82f8be03a0f7bd703","tid":1535441,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27ff562dd2c2b2c4b24b939f8f30db9eb9f8170a","tid":1535441,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2903586?fbclid=IwAR0f8co2XkVZnbh5lE_5Hn0qgoOw6EQDk7Knfx_SQ8eD0T2Xv4mlafyHkBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2903586%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0f8co2XkVZnbh5lE_5Hn0qgoOw6EQDk7Knfx_SQ8eD0T2Xv4mlafyHkBs&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=d0d20a00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2903586%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0f8co2XkVZnbh5lE_5Hn0qgoOw6EQDk7Knfx_SQ8eD0T2Xv4mlafyHkBs&h=c5fe8f1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2903586?fbclid=IwAR0f8co2XkVZnbh5lE_5Hn0qgoOw6EQDk7Knfx_SQ8eD0T2Xv4mlafyHkBs</a>"},{"pid":"65bc4bfd75c192efecf14d61abe8aa0c35aa1c13","tid":1535441,"uid":125680,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2acf7558b4f062badbee7788e27dd7ac45a52b91","tid":1535441,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/09/02/phpoDStFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2FphpoDStFV.jpg&h=0c71a6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕